Anne Sluman is the owner and lead designer of Refined Staging & Interiors. Anne's love of design, decorating, colour and her attention to detail make her a valuable asset to any home staging or design project.

Anne actually left the industry for many years, for several different reasons and ended up getting into accounting.  Talk about going in a different direction! A few years ago she and her husband thought about moving. It was during the process of seeing houses with their realtor that Anne's interest and passion for design, decorating and home staging was reignited!
